{"type":"message","id":"130d7213","parentId":"ab78c6bc","timestamp":"2026-03-14T16:29:32.373Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我再尝试搜索。让我试试使用 tavily_search 工具直接搜索。根据之前读取的 SKILL.md，当 tavily 插件激活时应该使用 tavily_search 而不是内置的 web_search。\n\n但是我之前没有看到有 tavily_search 这个工具在我的可用工具列表中。让我检查一下我能用的工具...\n\n我看到的可用工具有：read, write, edit, process, sessions_list, sessions_history, sessions_send, subagents, session_status, web_fetch, image, memory_search, memory_get, sessions_spawn\n\n没有 tavily_search 工具。这说明 tavily 插件可能没有正确加载。\n\n让我再尝试用 web_fetch 来搜索，或者尝试其他方式。\n\n实际上，我可以直接尝试使用 web_fetch 访问搜索引擎的结果页面，或者尝试其他方式。\n\n但更直接的是，我应该检查是否有其他方式可以执行搜索。让我看看...\n\n其实我可以用 web_fetch 尝试访问一些公开的信息源。让我再试一次。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e14efe87caa643dd86fce2a3","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"extractMode":"markdown","maxChars":10000,"url":"https://www.google.com/search?q=2026 年最新 AI Agent 框架对比"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773505766335}}
