)\\n\\n- [Discussions](/triggerdotdev/trigger.dev/discussions)\\n\\n Trigger.dev – build and deploy fully‑managed AI agents and workflows\\n\\n- Updated\\n Mar 14, 2026\\n\\n- TypeScript\\n\\n- [Code](/VoltAgent/awesome-claude-code-subagents)\\n\\n- [Issues](/VoltAgent/awesome-claude-code-subagents/issues)\\n\\n- [Pull requests](/VoltAgent/awesome-claude-code-subagents/pulls)\\n\\n A collection of 100+ specialized Claude Code subagents covering a wide range of development use cases\\n\\n- Updated\\n Mar 3, 2026\\n\\n- Shell\\n\\n- [Code](/crestalnetwork/intentkit)\\n\\n- [Issues](/crestalnetwork/intentkit/issues)\\n\\n- [Pull requests](/crestalnetwork/intentkit/pulls)\\n\\n- [Discussions](/crestalnetwork/intentkit/discussions)\\n\\n IntentKit is an open-source, self-hosted cloud agent cluster that manages a collaborative team of AI agents for you.\\n\\n- Updated\\n Mar 13, 2026\\n\\n- Python\\n\\n- [Code](/MervinPraison/PraisonAI)\\n\\n- [Issues](/MervinPraison/PraisonAI/issues)\\n\\n- [Pull requests](/MervinPraison/PraisonAI/pulls)\\n\\n- [Discussions](/MervinPraison/PraisonAI/discussions)\\n\\n PraisonAI 🦞 - Your 24/7 AI employee team. Automate and solve complex challenges with low-code multi-agent AI that plans, researches, codes, and delivers to Telegram, Discord, and WhatsApp. Handoffs, guardrails, memory, RAG, 100+ LLMs.\\n\\n- Updated\\n Mar 14, 2026\\n\\n- Python\\n\\n- [Code](/Intelligent-Internet/ii-agent)\\n\\n- [Issues](/Intelligent-Internet/ii-agent/issues)\\n\\n- [Pull requests](/Intelligent-Internet/ii-agent/pulls)\\n\\n II-Agent: a new open-source framework to build and deploy intelligent agents\\n\\n- Updated\\n Feb 4, 2026\\n\\n- Python\\n\\n- [Code](/jim-schwoebel/awesome_ai_agents)\\n\\n- [Issues](/jim-schwoebel/awesome_ai_agents/issues)\\n\\n- [Pull requests](/jim-schwoebel/awesome_ai_agents/pulls)\\n\\n 🤖 A comprehensive list of 1,500+ resources and tools related to AI agents.\\n\\n- Updated\\n Dec 17, 2025\\n\\n- [Code](/inngest/agent-kit)\\n\